{"type":"message","id":"8e5bb9ce","parentId":"32b626e1","timestamp":"2026-03-23T08:06:51.758Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了 cron.md，让我读取它来了解如何设置定时任务。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_txv4dkeips1j_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\linkang\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\cli\\cron.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774253207245}}
{"type":"message","id":"4109af1d","parentId":"8e5bb9ce","timestamp":"2026-03-23T08:06:51.769Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_txv4dkeips1j_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nsummary: \"CLI reference for `openclaw cron` (schedule and run background jobs)\"\nread_when:\n  - You want scheduled jobs and wakeups\n  - You’re debugging cron execution and logs\ntitle: \"cron\"\n---\n\n# `openclaw cron`\n\nManage cron jobs for the Gateway scheduler.\n\nRelated:\n\n- Cron jobs: [Cron jobs](/automation/cron-jobs)\n\nTip: run `openclaw cron --help` for the full command surface.\n\nNote: isolated `cron add` jobs default to `--announce` delivery. Use `--no-deliver` to keep\noutput internal. `--deliver` remains as a deprecated alias for `--announce`.\n\nNote: one-shot (`--at`) jobs delete after success by default. Use `--keep-after-run` to keep them.\n\nNote: recurring jobs now use exponential retry backoff after consecutive errors (30s → 1m → 5m → 15m → 60m), then return to normal schedule after the next successful run.\n\nNote: `openclaw cron run` now returns as soon as the manual run is queued for execution. Successful responses include `{ ok: true, enqueued: true, runId }`; use `openclaw cron runs --id <job-id>` to follow the eventual outcome.\n\nNote: retention/pruning is controlled in config:\n\n- `cron.sessionRetention` (default `24h`) prunes completed isolated run sessions.\n- `cron.runLog.maxBytes` + `cron.runLog.keepLines` prune `~/.openclaw/cron/runs/<jobId>.jsonl`.\n\nUpgrade note: if you have older cron jobs from before the current delivery/store format, run\n`openclaw doctor --fix`. Doctor now normalizes legacy cron fields (`jobId`, `schedule.cron`,\ntop-level delivery fields, payload `provider` delivery aliases) and migrates simple\n`notify: true` webhook fallback jobs to explicit webhook delivery when `cron.webhook` is\nconfigured.\n\n## Common edits\n\nUpdate delivery settings without changing the message:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw cron edit <job-id> --announce --channel telegram --to \"123456789\"\n```\n\nDisable delivery for an isolated job:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw cron edit <job-id> --no-deliver\n```\n\nEnable lightweight bootstrap context for an isolated job:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw cron edit <job-id> --light-context\n```\n\nAnnounce to a specific channel:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw cron edit <job-id> --announce --channel slack --to \"channel:C1234567890\"\n```\n\nCreate an isolated job with lightweight bootstrap context:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw cron add \\\n  --name \"Lightweight morning brief\" \\\n  --cron \"0 7 * * *\" \\\n  --session isolated \\\n  --message \"Summarize overnight updates.\" \\\n  --light-context \\\n  --no-deliver\n```\n\n`--light-context` applies to isolated agent-turn jobs only. For cron runs, lightweight mode keeps bootstrap context empty instead of injecting the full workspace bootstrap set.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774253211766}}
{"type":"message","id":"747d124f","parentId":"4109af1d","timestamp":"2026-03-23T08:06:59.849Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到了 cron 的用法。现在我需要创建一个定时任务，在每天 11:30 推送小红书热度榜单。\n\n按照文档，我需要使用 `openclaw cron add` 命令。让我创建一个命令来添加这个定时任务。\n\n问题是，这个任务需要执行 Python 脚本来获取小红书数据。我需要：\n1. 创建一个 Python 脚本输出消息\n2. 使用 cron 定时执行这个脚本并推送结果\n\n实际上，更好的方式是让这个 cron 任务调用一个脚本，然后通过 OpenClaw 的消息功能发送结果。\n\n让我看看有没有更好的方式。我可以创建一个 Python 脚本，然后通过 cron 执行它。\n\n实际上，按照文档说明，我应该使用 `--session isolated` 模式，然后让 cron 任务调用一个消息。让我试试创建一个 cron 任务。\n\n但是这个任务需要调用 Python 脚本。让我看看怎么做。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bjwdol36vs3c_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add --help","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774253211771}}
{"type":"message","id":"8d5d52fd","parentId":"747d124f","timestamp":"2026-03-23T08:07:04.207Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_bjwdol36vs3c_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Config warnings:\\n- plugins.entries.feishu: plugin feishu: duplicate plugin id detected; later plugin may be overridden (C:\\Users\\linkang\\.openclaw\\extensions\\feishu\\index.ts)\nConfig warnings:\\n- plugins.entries.feishu: plugin feishu: duplicate plugin id detected; later plugin may be overridden (C:\\Users\\linkang\\.openclaw\\extensions\\feishu\\index.ts)\n\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — Your terminal just grew claws—type something and let the bot pinch the busywork.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron add|create [options]\n\nAdd a cron job\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id for delivery (multi-account setups)\n  --agent <id>           Agent id for this job\n  --announce             Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style) (default:\n                         false)\n  --at <when>            Run once at time (ISO) or +duration (e.g. 20m)\n  --best-effort-deliver  Do not fail the job if delivery fails (default: false)\n  --channel <channel>    Delivery channel (last) (default: \"last\")\n  --cron <expr>          Cron expression (5-field or 6-field with seconds)\n  --delete-after-run     Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --deliver              Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to a\n                         chat.\n  --description <text>   Optional description\n  --disabled             Create job disabled (default: false)\n  --every <duration>     Run every duration (e.g. 10m, 1h)\n  --exact                Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0) (default:\n                         false)\n  --expect-final         Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output JSON (default: false)\n  --keep-after-run       Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --light-context        Use lightweight bootstrap context for agent jobs\n                         (default: false)\n  --message <text>       Agent message payload\n  --model <model>        Model override for agent jobs (provider/model or alias)\n  --name <name>          Job name\n  --no-deliver           Disable announce delivery and skip main-session summary\n  --session <target>     Session target (main|isolated)\n  --session-key <key>    Session key for job routing (e.g.\n                         agent:my-agent:my-session)\n  --stagger <duration>   Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\n  --system-event <text>  System event payload (main session)\n  --thinking <level>     Thinking level for agent jobs\n                         (off|minimal|low|medium|high|xhigh)\n  --timeout <ms>         Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\n  --timeout-seconds <n>  Timeout seconds for agent jobs\n  --to <dest>            Delivery destination (E.164, Telegram chatId, or\n                         Discord channel/user)\n  --token <token>        Gateway token (if required)\n  --tz <iana>            Timezone for cron expressions (IANA) (default: \"\")\n  --url <url>            Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to gateway.remote.url\n                         when configured)\n  --wake <mode>          Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat) (default: \"now\")"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":4349,"aggregated":"Config warnings:\\n- plugins.entries.feishu: plugin feishu: duplicate plugin id detected; later plugin may be overridden (C:\\Users\\linkang\\.openclaw\\extensions\\feishu\\index.ts)\nConfig warnings:\\n- plugins.entries.feishu: plugin feishu: duplicate plugin id detected; later plugin may be overridden (C:\\Users\\linkang\\.openclaw\\extensions\\feishu\\index.ts)\n\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — Your terminal just grew claws—type something and let the bot pinch the busywork.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron add|create [options]\n\nAdd a cron job\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id for delivery (multi-account setups)\n  --agent <id>           Agent id for this job\n  --announce             Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style) (default:\n                         false)\n  --at <when>            Run once at time (ISO) or +duration (e.g. 20m)\n  --best-effort-deliver  Do not fail the job if delivery fails (default: false)\n  --channel <channel>    Delivery channel (last) (default: \"last\")\n  --cron <expr>          Cron expression (5-field or 6-field with seconds)\n  --delete-after-run     Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --deliver              Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to a\n                         chat.\n  --description <text>   Optional description\n  --disabled             Create job disabled (default: false)\n  --every <duration>     Run every duration (e.g. 10m, 1h)\n  --exact                Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0) (default:\n                         false)\n  --expect-final         Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output JSON (default: false)\n  --keep-after-run       Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --light-context        Use lightweight bootstrap context for agent jobs\n                         (default: false)\n  --message <text>       Agent message payload\n  --model <model>        Model override for agent jobs (provider/model or alias)\n  --name <name>          Job name\n  --no-deliver           Disable announce delivery and skip main-session summary\n  --session <target>     Session target (main|isolated)\n  --session-key <key>    Session key for job routing (e.g.\n                         agent:my-agent:my-session)\n  --stagger <duration>   Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\n  --system-event <text>  System event payload (main session)\n  --thinking <level>     Thinking level for agent jobs\n                         (off|minimal|low|medium|high|xhigh)\n  --timeout <ms>         Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\n  --timeout-seconds <n>  Timeout seconds for agent jobs\n  --to <dest>            Delivery destination (E.164, Telegram chatId, or\n                         Discord channel/user)\n  --token <token>        Gateway token (if required)\n  --tz <iana>            Timezone for cron expressions (IANA) (default: \"\")\n  --url <url>            Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to gateway.remote.url\n                         when configured)\n  --wake <mode>          Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat) (default: \"now\")","cwd":"C:\\Users\\linkang\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774253224203}}
{"type":"message","id":"bce52f3b","parentId":"8d5d52fd","timestamp":"2026-03-23T08:07:16.656Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"明白了！用 cron 创建一个定时任务，每天 11:30 执行推送。但是这个需要调用 Python 脚本并把结果发到飞书。\n\n我需要创建一个 cron job，让它运行 Python 脚本，然后把输出发到飞书。\n\n实际上，更简单的方式是直接用 cron 的 message 功能，但 cron 似乎只能发固定消息。我需要让 cron 运行一个脚本，然后获取结果再发到飞书。\n\n让我看看怎么实现。实际上，cron 可以运行 Python 脚本，但需要把输出发给用户。最简单的方式是：\n1. 创建一个 Python 脚本，生成消息\n2. 让 cron 调用这个脚本\n3. 但是如何把消息发给飞书呢？\n\n实际上可以用 cron 的 --message 功能，让它发一条消息给用户，然后我可以写一个更完整的脚本作为工具调用...\n\n等等，我可以直接创建一个 cron job，让它运行 Python 脚本，但是需要把输出发送到飞书。\n\n最简单的方案：\n1. 写一个 Python 脚本，获取热度Top5，然后调用飞书 API 发送消息\n2. 但是飞书需要通过 OpenClaw 的 message 工具发送\n\n更好的方案是：\n\n\n我可以创建一个 cron job，直接发送一条消息给用户，然后消息内容可以是一个提示，让我知道需要运行推送脚本。但这不够自动化。\n\n或者，我可以使用 cron 的 --message 功能发送一个提示，然后由我（AI）来执行推送。但这也不是全自动的。\n\n最优雅的方案应该是创建一个 Python 脚本，获取热度信息并打印消息，然后用 cron 定时执行脚本，最后通过某种方式将输出推送到飞书。\n\n我可以创建一个独立的 Python 脚本，使用 feishu_doc 或 feishu_app_scopes 的 API 来发送消息，但这样比较复杂。\n\n让我先尝试用 cron 直接发送一条简单的消息测试一下。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_j2gjp9jrejxi_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add --name \"小红书旅游热度推送\" --cron \"30 11 * * 1-5\" --tz \"Asia/Shanghai\" --channel feishu --to \"ou_e48f6c4c0395f45b74b51525f348678b\" --message \"测试 cron\" --session isolated","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774253224209}}
