{"type":"message","id":"1bc35790","parentId":"9e53e42e","timestamp":"2026-03-23T08:07:47.205Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Cron job 创建成功了！现在需要把实际的小红书推送脚本配置进去。但是 isolated session 模式下，需要把脚本放到某个地方让它执行。\n\n让我修改 cron job 的消息内容，让它调用实际的脚本。或者，我可以在 workspace 里创建一个脚本，然后让 cron 运行时调用它。\n\n实际上，更好的方式是让 cron job 触发一个 agent turn，然后 agent 执行 Python 脚本并发送消息。\n\n让我先创建一个更完整的脚本，然后修改 cron job。"},{"type":"text","text":"Cron 创建成功！但需要改成调用实际的推送脚本。我来更新一下：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fjaql0kzpow1_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\linkang\\.openclaw\\workspace\\xiaohongshu_push.py","content":"#小红书旅游热度每日推送 - 完整版\nimport requests, json, sys, os\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\nsys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8')\n\n# MCP 地址\nMCP_URL = 'http://localhost:18060/mcp'\n\ndef init_mcp():\n    s = requests.Session()\n    hdrs = {'Accept':'application/json, text/event-stream'}\n    r1 = s.post(MCP_URL, json={'jsonrpc':'2.0','id':1,'method':'initialize','params':{'protocolVersion':'2024-11-05','capabilities':{},'clientInfo':{'name':'openclaw','version':'1.0'}}}, headers=hdrs)\n    hdrs['Mcp-Session-Id'] = r1.headers['Mcp-Session-Id']\n    s.post(MCP_URL, json={'jsonrpc':'2.0','method':'notifications/initialized'}, headers=hdrs)\n    return s, hdrs\n\ndef get_hot_notes(s, hdrs):\n    resp = s.post(MCP_URL, json={'jsonrpc':'2.0','id':2,'method':'tools/call','params':{'name':'search_feeds','arguments':{'keyword':'旅游','filters':{'sort_by':'综合'}}}}, headers=hdrs)\n    data = resp.json()\n    feeds = json.loads(data['result']['content'][0]['text'])['feeds']\n    \n    results = []\n    for f in feeds:\n        if f.get('modelType') == 'note' and len(results) < 5:\n            card = f.get('noteCard', {})\n            interact = card.get('interactInfo', {})\n            results.append({\n                'title': card.get('displayTitle', '无标题')[:35],\n                'likes': interact.get('likedCount', '0'),\n                'collects': interact.get('collectedCount', '0'),\n                'author': card.get('user', {}).get('nickname', ''),\n            })\n    return results\n\ndef build_message(results):\n    date = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n    msg = f\"📊 小红书旅游热度Top5（{date}）\\n\\n\"\n    for i, r in enumerate(results, 1):\n        msg += f\"{i}. {r['title']}\\n\"\n        msg += f\"   👍{r['likes']} | ⭐{r['collects']} | @{r['author']}\\n\\n\"\n    msg += \"---每日11:30自动推送\"\n    return msg\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    try:\n        s, hdrs = init_mcp()\n        results = get_hot_notes(s, hdrs)\n        msg = build_message(results)\n        print(msg)\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"获取失败: {e}\")\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774253250386}}
