{"type":"message","id":"fec8efb5","parentId":"b8b6d7d0","timestamp":"2026-03-23T09:01:30.182Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了！有几个相关的笔记：\n\n1. MiniMax API Key 避坑指南 - 👍42 | ⭐82\n2. (2/100) 编程小白minimax api配置 踩坑心得 - 👍14 | ⭐26\n3. 如何用OpenClaw配 MiniMax订阅计划 - 👍8 | ⭐12\n4. OpenClaw 买minimax套餐的api咋不对 - 👍29 | ⭐24\n\n让我获取第一条的详情来看看内容。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kb7b28scraef_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\linkang\\.openclaw\\workspace\\search_minimax.py","content":"import requests, json, sys, time\nsys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8')\ns = requests.Session()\nhdrs = {'Accept':'application/json, text/event-stream'}\nr1 = s.post('http://localhost:18060/mcp', json={'jsonrpc':'2.0','id':1,'method':'initialize','params':{'protocolVersion':'2024-11-05','capabilities':{},'clientInfo':{'name':'openclaw','version':'1.0'}}}, headers=hdrs)\nhdrs['Mcp-Session-Id'] = r1.headers['Mcp-Session-Id']\ns.post('http://localhost:18060/mcp', json={'jsonrpc':'2.0','method':'notifications/initialized'}, headers=hdrs)\n\n# 获取第一条详情\nresp = s.post('http://localhost:18060/mcp', json={'jsonrpc':'2.0','id':2,'method':'tools/call','params':{'name':'search_feeds','arguments':{'keyword':'MiniMax API Key 避坑'}}}, headers=hdrs)\ndata = resp.json()\nfeeds = json.loads(data['result']['content'][0]['text'])['feeds']\n\nfor f in feeds:\n    if f.get('modelType') == 'note':\n        card = f.get('noteCard', {})\n        if '避坑' in card.get('displayTitle', ''):\n            note_id = f.get('id')\n            token = f.get('xsecToken')\n            time.sleep(2)\n            resp2 = s.post('http://localhost:18060/mcp', json={'jsonrpc':'2.0','id':3,'method':'tools/call','params':{'name':'get_feed_detail','arguments':{'feed_id':note_id,'xsec_token':token}}}, headers=hdrs, timeout=30)\n            note = json.loads(resp2.json()['result']['content'][0]['text'])['data']['note']\n            print(f\"标题: {note['title']}\")\n            print(f\"\\n内容:\\n{note['desc'][:2000]}\")\n            break"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774256465369}}
