{"type":"message","id":"7ab1bdb9","parentId":"93ac6e47","timestamp":"2026-03-23T12:27:37.169Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要一个完整的日报图片，把文字和图片信息都整合到一张图里。我需要：\n1. 用 MiniMax 生成一张空白日报模板/背景图\n2. 或者用 Python 把文字和图片合成到一张图上\n\n用 Python PIL 来合成会更灵活。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_tvq11qvjy758_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nfrom PIL import Image, ImageDraw, ImageFont\nimport os\n\n# 创建空白画布\nwidth, height = 800, 1200\nimg = Image.new('RGB', (width, height), '#f5f5f5')\ndraw = ImageDraw.Draw(img)\n\n# 标题\ndraw.rectangle([(0, 0), (width, 120)], fill='#1a73e8')\ndraw.text((40, 40), '📊 小红书旅游热度日报', fill='white', size=36)\ndraw.text((40, 80), '2026年3月23日', fill='white', size=20)\n\n# 内容\ny = 150\ncontent = [\n    ('1️⃣ 3-4月旅行清单 | 8个目的地', '👍1954  ⭐1511  @🌸娜娜爱分享🌸', '春季出行推荐，人少性价比高'),\n    ('2️⃣ 度假目的地推荐（中）', '👍230  ⭐130  @双份十二月', '休闲度假式旅行目的地分享'),\n    ('3️⃣ 3.18九寨沟实况', '👍231  ⭐271  @用户已注销', '淡季九寨沟依然绝美'),\n    ('4️⃣ 贵州贵安樱花园', '👍1452  ⭐642  @烦遇', '《国家地理》推荐，世界最大樱花海'),\n    ('5️⃣ 花蓮不宜人類居住', '👍13579  ⭐2839  @弛隅', '超热门内容'),\n]\n\nfor title, stats, desc in content:\n    # 标题\n    draw.text((40, y), title, fill='black', size=24)\n    y += 35\n    # 热度\n    draw.text((40, y), stats, fill='gray', size=16)\n    y += 30\n    # 描述\n    draw.text((40, y), desc, fill='#666', size=18)\n    y += 50\n\n# 趋势洞察\ndraw.rectangle([(40, y+20), (width-40, y+120)], fill='#e8f5e9')\ndraw.text((60, y+35), '💡 趋势洞察', fill='#2e7d32', size=20)\ndraw.text((60, y+65), '春季赏花游（樱花、桃花）+ 九寨沟持续火热', fill='#2e7d32', size=16)\n\n# 保存\nimg.save(r'C:\\Users\\linkang\\.openclaw\\workspace\\daily_report_card.png')\nprint('done')\n\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774268839102}}
